### Synergy
- Batched rendering + adaptive frame scheduling = Ultra-smooth even with huge populations
- Low FPS mode + quantized food batching = Graceful degradation
- Headless builds + warning fixes = Clean CI/CD logs

## Future Enhancements

**Rendering optimizations**:
- GPU instancing for agent bodies (single draw call for all agents)
- Texture atlas for food cells (eliminate per-cell binning)
- Compute shader pre-culling (GPU-side viewport culling)
