**Food cell improvements**:
- Full-frame binning instead of per-row (fewer bins needed)
- Adaptive bin count based on visible color range
- Temporal coherence (reuse bins across frames)

**Memory optimizations**:
- Path builder pooling (reuse allocations across frames)
- GPU buffer reuse for static geometry
- Culling optimization (spatial hash for agents)

